#

Truffle Aioli Wagyu Beef Burger

$25.99
850 kcal
Difficulty: 70%

Allergens:

DairyEggs

Dietary Tags:

Gluten-FreeHigh-Protein

Tags:

GourmetLuxuryBeefBurger

Description

Indulge in a luxurious Wagyu burger topped with rich truffle aioli, creamy Gruyère, and sweet caramelized onions for an unforgettable culinary experience.

Ingredients

  • Wagyu beef patties: 2 (6 oz each)
  • Gruyère cheese: 4 slices
  • Brioche burger buns: 2
  • Truffle oil: 2 tablespoons
  • Mayonnaise: 1/2 cup
  • Garlic cloves: 2, minced
  • Yellow onion: 1, sliced
  • Butter: 2 tablespoons
  • Salt: to taste
  • Black pepper: to taste
  • Arugula: 1 cup
